{"text_id":17979,"tokens":["##"," Angular"," Rate"," Sensor","\n\n","**","Angular"," rate"," sensors","**,"," also"," known"," as"," gy","ros","copes"," or"," angular"," rate"," detectors",","," are"," devices"," that"," measure"," the"," rotational"," velocity"," of"," a"," rigid"," body"," about"," an"," arbitrary"," axis","."," They"," are"," essential"," for"," applications"," where"," precise"," angular"," measurements"," are"," required",","," such"," as"," robotics",","," aerospace"," engineering",","," and"," automotive"," engineering",".","\n\n","**","Principle"," of"," Operation",":**","\n\n","Angular"," rate"," sensors"," utilize"," different"," physical"," principles"," to"," detect"," angular"," motion","."," Some"," common"," types"," include",":","\n\n","*"," **","Mechanical"," gy","ros","copes",":**"," Use"," rotating"," masses"," and"," centrifugal"," forces"," to"," measure"," angular"," velocity",".","\n","*"," **","Vibr","ating"," gy","ros","copes",":**"," Employ"," vibrating"," plates"," or"," discs"," whose"," resonant"," frequency"," changes"," based"," on"," the"," applied"," angular"," velocity",".","\n","*"," **","Solid","-","state"," gy","ros","copes",":**"," Utilize"," the"," Cor","iolis"," effect"," on"," moving"," charges"," or"," currents"," to"," measure"," angular"," velocity",".","\n\n\n","**","Types",":**","\n\n","*"," **","Bia","xial",":**"," Measure"," angular"," velocity"," along"," two"," axes",".","\n","*"," **","Tri","axial",":**"," Measure"," angular"," velocity"," along"," all"," three"," axes",".","\n","*"," **","Digital",":**"," Output"," digital"," signals"," for"," ease"," of"," inter","facing"," with"," electronic"," systems",".","\n","*"," **","Analog",":**"," Output"," analog"," signals"," proportional"," to"," the"," angular"," velocity",".","\n\n\n","**","Applications",":**","\n\n","Angular"," rate"," sensors"," have"," numerous"," applications",","," including",":","\n\n","*"," **","Robotics",":**"," Precise"," navigation"," and"," stability"," control",".","\n","*"," **","Aeros","pace",":**"," Attitude"," determination",","," stability"," control",","," and"," navigation",".","\n","*"," **","Automotive",":**"," Stability"," control",","," traction"," control",","," and"," electronic"," stability"," programs",".","\n","*"," **","Consumer"," electronics",":**"," Gy","roscopic"," stabilization"," in"," devices"," like"," smartphones"," and"," cameras",".","\n\n\n","**","Advantages",":**","\n\n","*"," High"," precision"," and"," accuracy","\n","*"," Compact"," and"," lightweight"," designs","\n","*"," Digital"," output"," for"," easy"," integration"," with"," electronic"," systems","\n","*"," High"," resistance"," to"," shock"," and"," vibration","\n\n\n","**","Disadvantages",":**","\n\n","*"," Limited"," measurement"," range","\n","*"," Sus","ceptible"," to"," magnetic"," fields","\n","*"," Can"," be"," affected"," by"," temperature"," changes","\n\n","**","Future",":**","\n\n","Angular"," rate"," sensors"," are"," expected"," to"," continue"," to"," advance",","," offering"," improved"," accuracy",","," wider"," measurement"," ranges",","," and"," lower"," costs","."],"sub_source":"wikipedia","model":"gemma-7b-it","label":1}